description._content: Description: ############################################################################################################################################################################################################################################################### Location: Cyprus Date: 1926 Description: Forestry Exhibition, 1928, showing seedling forest trees and a Turkish and a Christian girl carrying pots. Location: Cyprus Date: 1928 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
